args: apt-get update         && apt-get install -y build-essential crossbuild-essential-${ARCH} squashfs-tools curl         && apt-get clean
(         for F in ${ENABLE_FEATURES};         do                 sed -i "s/^.*# CONFIG_${F} is not set.*$/CONFIG_${F}=y/" .config ;         done; )
env: ENABLE_FEATURES=LONG_OPTS SHOW_USAGE FEATURE_VERBOSE_USAGE FEATURE_COMPRESS_USAGE INSTALL_APPLET_HARDLINKS LFS INSTALL_NO_USR                 SV SVC SVOK SVLOGD RUNSV RUNSVDIR CHPST WATCHDOG
